00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,000
Every day, Lily packed her dad the same lunch, one peanut butter sandwich, an apple, and a little

2
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:11,000
note that said, have a great day, dad. She started doing it when she was eight, just for fun.

3
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:19,000
He never missed a day bringing it to work. Years passed. One day, Lily moved away for college.

4
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:26,000
She forgot all about the lunch routine. A week later, she got a package in the mail.

5
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:31,000
Inside was a half-eaten peanut butter sandwich, an apple, and a new note.

6
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:35,000
I miss you too, kiddo. But I'll be okay.

7
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:43,000
Go live your dream. She cried. But she smiled too, because love sometimes comes wrapped in bread and

8
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:50,000
paper.

